Distilleries Co. of Sri Lanka Plc
said one of its units bought a 47 percent stake in  Pelwatte
Sugar Industries Plc (SUGA)  at 27.5 rupees a share, according to a
filing to the  Colombo Stock Exchange  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
